      • generate

        Key generate(int pow2Max)
        パラメータ:
        pow2Max - power 2 of the max integer value
        戻り値:
        a new random key where its integer value is between 0 and 2^pow2Max - 1

      • get

        Key get(byte[] bytes)
        Convert a given byte array to a key. May throw an IllegalArgumentException if the number of bytes is incorrect.
        パラメータ:
        bytes - the key's bytes
        戻り値:
        a key with the given bytes

      • get

        パラメータ:

        戻り値:

      • create

        Key create(java.lang.String... topics)
        Create a new key from an array of topics. If 2 arrays of topics are equals then the 2 keys generated from them will be equal If 2 arrays of topics are not equals the chances of the keys to be equal are next to none
        パラメータ:
        topics - an arbitrary array of strings
        戻り値:
        a key corresponding to the topics array
